3815                                  'Reverting back to base model (NMIR) and solve successfully. ' /
3816                                  'Objective function value: ' NETBENEFIT.l:<15:4 /
3817                                  'Violations cost         : '  TOTALPENALTYCOST.l:<15:4 /
3818                                  'Solution may have circulating flows and/or non-physical losses.' /
